      "raw_text": "WASHINGTON, June S.-A dele\ncation of merchants from Muskogee,\nl. T., arrived today to protest to the\npresident and secretary of the in\nterror against the collection of the\ntribal tax assessed against white men\nfor doing business in the territory.\nThey ask delay in collection to take\nthe case to the supreme court."
